Popl_Jan18_USFOR_407_USFOR: Popl est., Landscan using USFOR-A 407 district set. (2)

Popl_est_2017_iMMAP_399_AGCHO: iMMAP's 2017 population estimates (5).  (They already follow the 399 district set, natively.)
